  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "### 2. Postulado de la Tétrada (Signos de Derivada)\n\nVerifica que la asignación dinámica de signos (`+1` para M, `-1` para Internal) aplique signos correctos en la expansión.",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "DefCovD[CD, M];\nFormat[CD[idx_]] := DisplayForm[SubscriptBox[\"\\\\[PartialD]\", IndexLabel[idx]]];\n\nDefTensorF[GammaAff[-a, -b, c], M]; SetDisplayName[GammaAff, \"\\\\[CapitalGamma]\"];\nDefTensorF[omegaSpin[-a, -II, JJ], {M, Internal}]; SetDisplayName[omegaSpin, \"\\\\[Omega]\"];\n\nDefineCovariantDerivative[D, CD, <| M -> {GammaAff, 1}, Internal -> {omegaSpin, -1} |>];\n\nFormat[CovDOp[idx_][expr_]] := DisplayForm[\n  RowBox[{SubscriptBox[\"D\", IndexLabel[idx]], \"(\", ToBoxes[expr, TraditionalForm], \")\"}]\n];\n\nexpr2 = CovDOp[-mu][Vb[II, -nu]];\nPrint[\"Output A (Estado Inicial - inerte): \"];\nexpr2\nPrint[\"Output B (Estado Final - expansion con signos): \"];\nExpandDerivative[D[-mu][Vb[II, -nu]], D, <|M -> rho, Internal -> JJ|>]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-print-output\"><div class=\"wl-print-line\"><span class=\"wl-ps\">** </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrw9fvbj-8sohrr7\" data-page-width-em=\"59\" data-latex-b64=\"XG1hdGhybXtEZWZUZW5zb3J9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">DefTensor</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div><span class=\"wl-ps\">: Defining </span><span class=\"wl-ps\">tensor </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrw9fvbm-ank4l9h\" data-page-width-em=\"59\" data-latex-b64=\"XG1hdGhybXtHYW1tYUFmZn1cbGVmdCgtYSwtYixjXHJpZ2h0KQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\" style=\"margin-right:0.07778em;\">GammaAff</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div><span class=\"wl-ps\">. </span><span class=\"wl-ps\"></span></div></div>",
